        dc:description           "Figures 2–7. Cobitis oxycephala Chen YX & Chen YF, sp. nov., Nandujiang River, Ding’an, Hainan, China. 2. Holotype, IHB 0509273, lateral view. 3. IHB 0509274, lateral view. 4. Lamina circularis in the pectoral in of male, dorsal view. 5. Mouth characters, front view. 6. Suborbital spine, left dorsal view, right interior view. 7. Subdorsal scales, dorsal view. Scale bars: 2–3 =1 cm; 4–6 = 1mm; 7=100μm." ;
